"     Silvano Loperfido, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?25/38/26216/contributors\">",
"     Guido Costamagna, MD, FACG",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
